&S(9)    SETB  (T'&LXLIST NE 'O')       IF OPTION SPECIFIED SET BIT     07950000
         AIF   (T'&LXLIST EQ 'O').OK20  IF NOT, GO CHECK FORCE PARM     08000000
&OPERAND SETC  'LXLIST'                 SET FOR POSSIBLE ERROR MSGS     08050000
&OPVAL   SETC  '&LXLIST'                SET FOR POSSIBLE ERROR MSGS     08100000
.*   DETERMINE WHETHER LXLIST ADDRESS IS RX OR REG TYPE                 08150000
         AIF   ('&LXLIST'(1,1) EQ '(').OK11   BRANCH IF REG TYPE        08200000
